column6: Enjoy a private room and bathroom for two, conveniently located across the street from HEB and only a mile from Texas A&M University. Perfect for a quick weekend trip, new student conference, or overnight stay before heading off to fish camp. \nGuests will have access to free parking, the living room, washer, dryer, kitchen and coffee bar. \nPlease come to us with any questions you have while staying here. We will gladly offer places to eat or things to do!
